thread.title: Ciara K.
thread.title_full: Tony Kealys reviewed by Ciara K.

author: Ciara K.
title: Ciara K.
text: I don't live local to any branch so found the online chat service in finding a suitable car seat for my daughter very useful and informative, the team are very knowledgable and customer service is great. I have always heard great things about Tony Kealys so I wouldn't have shopped anywhere else for a car seat.
